        <abstract>
            <p>Wishes to subscribe to RM’s translation of Weismann.</p>
            <p>Has seen Scudder’s article.</p> 
<p>A. R. Wallace’s article ["Animals and their native countries", <hi rend="italic">Nineteenth Century</hi> 5 (1879): 247–59] is excellent.</p> 
        </abstract>
